import React from 'react';
import { Box } from '@mui/material';
import Header from './Header';  // Correctly import default export
import Hero from './Hero';  // Correctly import default export
import LoginSignup from './LoginSignup';  // Correctly import default export
import InfoSection from './InfoSection';  // Correctly import default export

function HomePage() {
  return (
    <Box sx={{ backgroundColor: '#f5f5f5', minHeight: '100vh', paddingTop: 8 }}>
      <Header />
      <Hero />
      <LoginSignup />
      <InfoSection
        title="How Catches Are Scored"
        content="Learn how our sophisticated scoring algorithm ensures fairness and accuracy."
        id="scoring"
      />
      <InfoSection
        title="How You Can Make Money"
        content="Discover how you can win cash prizes and other rewards by participating in tournaments."
        id="earnings"
      />
      <InfoSection
        title="Cheating Detection"
        content="Our advanced technology ensures a level playing field by detecting and preventing cheating."
        id="cheating"
      />
      <InfoSection
        title="A Seamless User Experience"
        content="Experience a smooth and intuitive interface designed for both novices and seasoned anglers."
        id="experience"
      />
    </Box>
  );
}

export default HomePage; // Ensure this is a default export
